import React from 'react'
import Home from './Components/Home'
import Navbar from './Components/Navbar'
import { Switch ,Route} from 'react-router-dom'

import "./style.css"
const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/" component={Home} />
      
    </Switch>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
